BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:o5CZ5gFSO4LWIZurS9KCl
SUMMARY:Kristian Bugge & Ruthie Dornfeld – 2 Fiddle masters play Danish & A
	merican music and more!
DTSTAMP:20260307T061518Z
DTSTART:20260307T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Kristian Bugge (Denmark) and Ruthie Dornfeld (Seattle) will ent
	ertain us with a wide range of music including Danish traditional fiddle t
	unes and music from the other Nordic countries to old-time American and se
	lf-composed original tunes\\\, spiced up with a few Venezuelan waltzes.\\n
	Kristian and Ruthie first met each other in the Danish folk music circles 
	in the mid-1990’s\\\, where Ruthie had been touring regularly and growing 
	a reputation as a well-renowned artist and fiddler since the early 1980’s.
	 Later when Kristian was a music student\\\, Ruthie was guest-teaching at 
	the Carl Nielsen Academy of Music in Odense\\\, Denmark and Kristian made 
	sure to take the opportunity to study with her while she was there. About 
	ten years later they met again in and around Seattle when Kristian had sta
	rted touring and performing in the states. This summer marked a new chapte
	r in their collaboration and friendship as they started touring and record
	ing as a duo for the first time. Expect everything from wild polkas and ji
	gs to lyrical waltzes\\\, fiery reels and happy hopsas\\\, all served with
	 humor and stories from their many years on the road. The doors open at 7p
	m for the 7:30 cocnert in the phinney Community Hall (lower Brick Building
	). Advance tickets are $26/$24 members of SFS\\\, PNA\\\, or Skandia\\\, s
	tudents\\\, or seniors 65+/ $10 Youth to age 17\; at the door $2 more for 
	adults ($28/$26/$10).\n\nhttps://www.phinneycenter.org/event/kristian-bugg
	e-ruthie-dornfeld-2-fiddle-masters-play-danish-american-music-and-more/\n\
	nFrom Phinney Neighborhood Association (PNA)
URL:https://www.phinneycenter.org/event/kristian-bugge-ruthie-dornfeld-2-fi
	ddle-masters-play-danish-american-music-and-more/
LOCATION:Phinney Center Campus\\\, 6532 Phinney Ave. N.\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\
	\\, 98103\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:phinney-neighborhood-association
CATEGORIES:Phinney Neighborhood Association (PNA)
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
