DESCRIPTION:Pause and see the natural world more closely through nature jou
	rnaling and botanical inks. In this gentle\\\, hands-on class\\\, you’ll l
	earn the basics of making ink from flowers and use these plant-based pigme
	nts to start a nature journal. You’ll also learn how considerations like p
	aper and additives can give you different and exciting colors. All materia
	ls are included and each participant will take home a small sketchbook tha
	t we make in class and a 15ml pot of handmade floral ink—an invitation to 
	notice new growth\\\, returning light\\\, and the unfolding of spring.\n\n
